bilingual.source: This may be driven partly by self-deception or "wishful thinking''.
bilingual.target: 这在一定程度上可能是由自欺欺人或"一厢情愿"促成的。

bilingual.source: This is partly driven by the rising price of raw materials and metals.
bilingual.target: 原材料和金属价格的上涨在一定程度上促使企业开始行动。

bilingual.source: My interest in cooking started when I was 11, partly thanks to my mother.
bilingual.target: 我从11岁开始对烹饪产生兴趣，这在一定程度上要归功于我的母亲。

bilingual.source: This is partly underpinned by commercial logic.
bilingual.target: 这在一定程度上得到了商业逻辑的支撑。

bilingual.source: But it was also partly the fault of the workplace.
bilingual.target: 但在一定程度上也要归咎于工作场所.

bilingual.source: Partly as a result, the competition is heating up.
bilingual.target: 这在一定程度上导致了竞争加剧.

bilingual.source: His attitudes were shaped partly by early experiences.
bilingual.target: 他的想法在一定程度上是由他早期的经历决定的。

bilingual.source: Researchers cautioned that the drug was only partly effective.
bilingual.target: 研究者警告说，这种药只在一定程度上有效。

bilingual.source: The award was partly a joke, but also partly real, and Jobs knew about it and liked it.
bilingual.target: 这个奖在一定程度上是个玩笑，但也有认真的意思，乔布斯知道这个奖并且还很喜欢它。

bilingual.source: The cylinder had been partly full, but the jet was blocked.
bilingual.target: 气缸已经在一定程度上充满了，但喷嘴却阻塞了。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. And he said really mean things that were only partly true.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说了一些很恶劣，又不尽真实的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross, look, I know I've been giving you a lot of jabs and it's partly because I'm very protective of Lizzie, and partly because well, they just keep coming to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯，我知道我一直找你麻烦，因为我很保护丽莎，而且你的缺点实在很多。

yingyinNormal.en: Because on the third day my mother killed herself so I was partly crying for that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三天我妈自杀了，我也在为那件事而哭。
